🔥 Production Scenario
Problem

An application deployment fails because of missing package dependencies.

Investigation

Update repositories:

sudo apt update

Fix broken packages:

sudo apt --fix-broken install

Check dependencies:

apt depends nginx

Check held packages:

apt-mark showhold

Verify installed version:

dpkg -s nginx
